# Cursor Rules – Academia Yael Rodríguez Landing

This file provides context and guidelines for Cursor AI when working on the Academia Yael Rodríguez beauty academy landing page.

## Project Overview

Landing page for **Yael Rodríguez Beauty & Business Academy** – formación integral en belleza (uñas, cejas, pestañas, estética). Static, SEO-optimized, Spanish-language. Blog-ready via Astro Content Collections (not implemented yet).

**Tech Stack:**
- **Framework:** Astro (static, SSG)
- **Styling:** TailwindCSS
- **Content:** Spanish only (no i18n initially)
- **DevOps:** Docker, docker-compose; production behind Traefik

## Architecture Patterns

### Astro
- Use `.astro` components; prefer static rendering
- Colocate components in `src/components/` by section
- Layouts in `src/layouts/`
- Pages in `src/pages/`
- Content Collections in `src/content/` (blog-ready)

### Tailwind
- Design tokens: `academy-pink` (#e298b4), `academy-dark` (#1a1a1a)
- Fonts: Playfair Display (serif), Montserrat (sans)
- Utility-first; use responsive utilities (`md:`, `lg:`)

## Design System

- **Colors:** academy-pink, academy-dark, white
- **Typography:** Playfair Display for headings, Montserrat for body
- **Components:** btn-outline (white border, hover fill), floral-bg (dark overlay), card-dark-translucent
- **Images:** Use `ImagePlaceholder.astro` for placeholders until real images provided

## SEO & Accessibility

- Semantic HTML: `header`, `main`, `section`, `footer`, correct h1–h6 hierarchy
- Single `<h1>` per page (brand name)
- Meta tags: title, description, Open Graph, Twitter cards
- JSON-LD: Organization, LocalBusiness, EducationalOrganization, Review
- Alt text for all images (including placeholders via aria-label)
- `lang="es"` on `<html>`
- Sitemap, robots.txt

## File Locations

| Area | Path |
|------|------|
| Components | `src/components/` |
| Layouts | `src/layouts/` |
| Pages | `src/pages/` |
| Content | `src/content/` (blog collection) |
| Styles | `src/styles/` |
| Public assets | `public/` |
| AI context | `ai/context/` |

## Important Rules

1. Use **Astro** for all components; TypeScript where applicable
2. Use **Tailwind** with design tokens (academy-pink, academy-dark)
3. **Image placeholders** – colored boxes with descriptive aria-label until real images
4. **SEO** – meta, schema, semantic HTML, alt text
5. **Spanish** – all copy in Spanish
6. After notable changes, update `ai/context/RECENT_CHANGES.md`

